# ConKeeper Memory System

When working on non-trivial tasks, use the ConKeeper memory system.

## Memory Location
`.claude/memory/`

## Available Workflows

### memory-init
Initialize memory: create `.claude/memory/` with product-context.md, active-context.md, progress.md, patterns.md, glossary.md, decisions/, sessions/

### memory-sync
Sync session: update active-context.md, progress.md, create ADRs for significant decisions

### session-handoff
Generate handoff prompt for seamless continuation in new session

## Usage
- Load memory at session start for non-trivial tasks
- Sync memory after significant progress
- Use handoff when context window fills
